reviewText: This DVD is a joke. It doesn't tell you anything that most people don't already know about installing carpet. You could probably get more information just searching online. It is only about 10 minutes long.
THIS IS ONE OF THE BEST WELL ILLUSTRATED TRAINING DVD'S I HAVE EVERY SEEN , AND I SEEN ALOT. ULTIMATE SHOW AND TELL OF HOW TO LAY CARPET AND WHAT YOU NEED TO GET IT DONE RIGHT !
